m%20in%20case%20she%20dropped%20her%20Asia%20tour%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMentally%2C%20I%20was%20already%20prepared%20to%20travel%20to%20see%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Taylor%20finally%20announced%20the%20international%20dates%20last%20year%2C%20she%20only%20had%20Tokyo%20and%20Singapore%20in%20Asia.%20Tokyo%20is%20too%20far%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20I'd%20try%20to%20catch%20her%20in%20Singapore%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBut%20buying%20tickets%20for%20her%20concert%20was%20tough%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20and%20I%20weren't%20able%20to%20get%20tickets%20through%20Ticketmaster%2C%20so%20I%20started%20looking%20for%20alternate%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20I%20learned%20that%20Klook%2C%20the%20booking%20platform%2C%20was%20launching%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Ftetris%2Fpromo%2Ftaylorswifttheerastoursg%2F%3Fspm%3DBlogArticle.InArticleHyperlinkWord%26clickId%3Deeab6be9ff%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEras%20Tour%20experience%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20included%20two%20concert%20tickets%20and%20a%20one-night%20hotel%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20went%20live%20on%20the%20Klook%20mobile%20app%20during%20Singapore%20time%2C%20and%20due%20to%20the%20time%20difference%2C%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20had%20to%20wake%20up%20early%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20clicking%20on%20the%20link%2C%20I%20was%20immediately%20sent%20into%20the%20waiting%20room.%20I%20think%20I%20was%209%2C000%20or%20something%20in%20the%20queue.%20It%20was%20a%20long%20shot%2C%20but%20I%20moved%20up%20the%20queue%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt%20felt%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20and%20I%20had%20looked%20through%20the%20packages%20prior%2C%20trying%20to%20see%20which%20would%20fit%20our%20budget%20best.%20But%20when%20I%20finally%20got%20to%20the%20page%2C%20the%20cheapest%20package%20was%20already%20sold%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20the%20concert%20date%20and%20the%20seats%20didn't%20matter%2