whales'%20behavior%2C%20but%20one%20explanation%20offered%20in%20the%20study%20was%20that%20Whale%20B%20was%20possibly%20exerting%20dominance%20over%20an%20injured%20rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20the%20first%20instance%20of%20homosexual%20activity%20being%20observed%20in%20animals%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgay-behaviors-common-monkeys-give-them-evolutionary-edge-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonkeys%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dolphins%2C%20and%20penguins%2C%20among%20others%2C%20known%20to%20have%20engaged%20in%20such%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20on%20another%20scientific%20breakthrough%20involving%20humpback%20whales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20were%20able%20to%20hold%20a%2020-minute%20%26quot%3Bconversation%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20humpback%20whale%20by%20emitting%20contact%20calls%20at%20varying%20intervals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20certainly%20felt%20like%20we%20had%20been%20heard%2C%26quot%3B%20Fred%20Sharpe%2C%20coauthor%20and%20principal%20investigator%20with%20the%20Alaska%20Whale%20Foundation%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20this%20is%20the%20first%20such%20communicative%20exchange%20between%20humans%20and%20humpback%20whales%20in%20the%20humpback%20'language%2C'%26quot%3B%20Brenda%20McCowan%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20UC%20Davis's%20School%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%2C%20added%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seti.org%2Fpress-release%2Fwhale-seti-groundbreaking-encounter-humpback-whales-reveals-potential-non-human-intelligence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20contacted%20the%20Pacific%20Whale%20Foundation%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmale-humpback-whales-photographed-having-sex-scientific-breakthrough-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness