BIt's%20just%20very%20easy%20and%20cheap%20to%20put%20the%20tech%20into%20other%20systems%2C%20which%20means%20they%20turn%20up%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20get%20more%20and%20more%20common.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20machines%20removed%20from%20the%20college%20campus%2C%20Russell%20said%20it%20didn't%20look%20as%20though%20they%20were%20actively%20using%20the%20facial%20recognition%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20error%20message%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20it's%20hooked%20into%20a%20huge%20bunch%20of%20additional%20code%20which%20could%20do%20facial%20recognition%20but%20is%20not%20turned%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAdvertising%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20knows%20for%20sure%20how%20widespread%20the%20use%20of%20facial%20recognition%20technology%20is%20%E2%80%94%20or%20how%20private%20companies%20are%20using%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20its%20most%20common%20use%20is%20likely%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvertising%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertising%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussell%20said%20the%20main%20advantage%20of%20installing%20the%20tech%20is%20being%20able%20to%20tell%20advertisers%20that%20ads%20are%20being%20personalized%20for%20specific%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20target%20particular%20ages%20and%20particular%20genders%2C%20and%20they%20can%20guarantee%20that%20they%20will%20start%20the%20ad%20as%20someone%20walks%20up%20the%20screen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20use%20the%20tech%20as%20a%20motion%20sensor%20rather%20than%20a%20sinister%20surveillance%20tactic.%20They%20are%20also%20not%20likely%20to%20be%20storing%20any%20data%20picked%20up%20from%20the%20facial%20recognition%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20smart%20vending%20machines%2C%20the%20company%20that%20provides%20them%20told%2