0years%20ahead%20of%20her%20plans%2C%20and%20it's%20paying%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOkwulehie%20said%20she%20was%20surprised%20Juntero%20Design%2C%20which%20she%20owns%20and%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20her%20and%20her%20husband's%20business%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.juntero.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuntero%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20become%20her%20main%20source%20of%20income.%20Juntero%20provides%20architecture%20services%20like%20designs%20and%203D%20models%20as%20well%20as%20non-architecture%20services%20like%20graphic%20design%20or%20photo%20editing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F7-side-hustles-that-will-earn-6-figures-or-more-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eside%20gigs%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20pretty%20much%20a%20hobby%20at%20first%20and%20an%20extra%20way%20she%20could%20explore%20design%20work%20outside%20of%20her%20job%20as%20a%20senior%20architect%20at%20the%20Port%20Authority%20of%20New%20York%20and%20New%20Jersey.%20She%20said%20her%20side%20work%20ranged%20from%20graphic%20design%2C%20photo%20editing%2C%20and%20web%20design%20to%20architecture%20and%20interior%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20doing%20a%20lot%20that%20first%20year.%20Once%20I%20started%20looking%20at%20the%20numbers%2C%20then%20I%20realized%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20people%20were%20more%20interested%20in%20architecture%2C%20interior%20design%2C%20which%20is%20what%20I%20studied%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20started%20focusing%20on%20that%20as%20a%20niche.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20she%20said%20her%20job%20for%20Port%20Authority%20%26quot%3Bis%20more%20like%20a%20side%20gig.%26quot%3B%20Instead%20of%20the%20typical%20split%20between%20a%209-to-5%20providing%20the%20bulk%20of%20one's%20income%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fside-hustle-recommendations-surveys-youtube-retirement-goal-house-truck-payment-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eside%20hustle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bin%20this%20case%2C%20it's%20the%20other%20way%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20documentation%20shared%20with%20BI%2C%20Okwulehie%20made%20over%20%24100%2C000%20in%202023%20from%20her%20job%20for%20the%20Port%20Authority.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Juntero%20Design%20had%20a%20gross%20income%20of%20more%20than%20%24400%2C000%20in%202023%20and%20a%20net%20profit%20that%20was%20still%20greater%20than%20her%20salary%20from%20Port%20Authority.%20Additionally%2C%20she%20drew%20a%20salary%20of%20%2437%2C500%20from%20the%20side%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOkwulehie%20is%20a%20supporter%20of%20diversifying%20your%20income%20streams%2C%20especially%20in%20today's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20any%20talent%20or%20trade%2C%20try%20your%20best%20to%20monetize%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Okwulehie%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20need%20to%20take%20on%20that%20extra%20work%2C%20maybe%20spend%20one%20or%20two%20hours%20in%20the%20morning%20on%20the%20weekends%20to%20just%20focus%20on%20your%20craft%20and%20then%20see%20where%20it%20takes%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20aims%20to%20provide%20her%20design%20services%20to%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20clients.%20Juntero%20has%20one-time%20payment%20models%20and%20also%20monthly%2C%20quarterly%2C%20or%20annual%20membership%20programs%20that%20Okwulehie%20finds%20could%20be%20helpful%20for%20developers%2C%20interior%20design%20firms%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20catered%20to%20the%20elites%2C%20it's%20more%20so%20catered%20to%20your%20regular%20homeowner%20who%20just%20needs%20something%20renovated%20in%20their%20home%20or%20just%20wants%20to%20visualize%20the%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20Juntero%20Design%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20potential%20clients%20because%20it%20was%20a%20one-stop%20shop%20where%20you%20can%20not%20only%20get%20architectural%20design%2C%20you%20can%20also%20get%20interior%20design%2C%20and%20you%20can%20actually%20visualize%20your%20project%20all%20in%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20Okwulehie's%20business%20has%20evolved%20and%20became%20more%20profitable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOkwulehie%20said%20her%20first%20side%20gig%20was%20a%20graphic%20design%20project%20for%20Indeed%20where%20she%20made%20several%20dollars%20%26quot%3Bto%20see%20how%20it%20feels%20to%20work%20with%20a%20client.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Juntero%20Design's%20revenue%20increased%20from%20around%20%2455%2C000%20in%202021%20to%20nearly%20%24206%2C000%20in%202022%20and%20over%20%24400%2C000%20last%20year%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20outsource%20most%20of%20the%20work%2C%20partly%20so%20she%20can%20help%20more%20clients%20given%20the%20extra%20assistance.%20Her%20process%20includes%20creating%20a%20concept%20that%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20the%20architects%2C%20designers%2C%20or%20whomever%20is%20taking%20on%20the%20project.%20Okwulehie%20will%20do%20quality%20assurance%20and%20control%20after%20the%20person%20does%20the%20production%20work%20and%20before%20a%20client%20sees%20it.%20She%20said%20she%20spends%20most%20of%20the%20time%20focusing%20on%20marketing%2C%20accounting%2C%20client%20management%2C%20and%20working%20with%20her%20lawyers%2C%20financial%20planner%2C%20and%20accountant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20a%20great%20thing%20about%20the%20work%20being%20outsourced%20is%20she%20can%20spend%20just%20a%20few%20hours%20a%20week%20on%20the%20business.%20Plus%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20has%20been%20able%20to%20attract%20more%20clients%20since%20I%20have%20more%20people%20helping.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20at%20first%20she%20was%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20work%20on%20her%20own%2C%20but%20noted%20it%20was%20interfering%20with%20her%20weekend%20given%20she%20had%20to%20do%20her%20full-time%20job%20during%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20interfering%20with%20my%20family%20time%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20take%20on%20as%20many%20projects%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20people%20may%20consider%20making%20a%20side%20gig%20into%20their%20full-time%20job%2C%20Okwulehie%20isn't%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20her%20senior%20architect%20role.%20She's%20been%20working%20for%20Port%20Authority%20for%20over%20six%20years%20and%20said%20she%20learns%20from%20her%20colleagues%20and%20enjoys%20having%20the%20chance%20to%20exchange%20ideas%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20working%20there%20has%20been%20great.%20Most%20of%20her%20projects%20are%20infrastructure%20ones%2C%20and%20she%20said%20designing%20and%20coordinating%20with%20different%20disciplines%20are%20two%20main%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELean%20on%20friends%20and%20your%20network%20to%20get%20started%20on%20monetizing%20your%20talents%20while%20also%20working%20a%20main%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20hoping%20to%20have%20the%20same%20success%20as%20Okwulehie%2C%20there%20are%20things%20people%20can%20do%20to%20get%20started%20on%20side%20work%20and%20to%20work%20toward%20making%20it%20their%20primary%20source%20of%20income.%20Okwulehie%20suggested%20starting%20small%20but%20making%20a%20goal%20about%20how%20much%20you%20want%20to%20earn.%20This%20could%20then%20be%20divided%20up%20to%20see%20how%20many%20weeks%20or%20months%20it%20will%20take%20to%20get%20there%20and%20how%20much%20you%20will%20have%20to%20charge%20for%20work.%20Okwulehie%20said%20you%20can%20start%20small%20in%20terms%20of%20your%20rate%2C%20and%20then%20can%20raise%20this%20as%20you%20take%20on%20more%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it's%20an%20hourly%20job%20or%20a%20fixed-rate%20job%2C%20start%20steadily%20increasing%20it%20maybe%20every%20six%20to%2012%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Okwulehie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOkwulehie%20said%20she%20gradually%20raised%20her%20hourly%20rate%20and%20rates%20per%20job%20%26quot%3Bdepending%20on%20whether%20it's%20a%20fixed-rate%20contract%20or%20hourly%20rate%20contract.%26quot%3B%20She%20noted%20most%20of%20her%20work%20is%20done%20on%20fixed-rate%20contracts%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20considering%20monetizing%20your%20talent%20or%20looking%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20would%20be%20a%20good%20side%20hustle%20for%20you%2C%20Okwulehie%20said%20to%20use%20both%20professional%20and%20personal%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOkwulehie%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20checking%20if%20a%20friend%20needs%20help%20making%20a%20website.%20She%20suggested%20taking%20the%20gig%20even%20if%20the%20pay%20isn't%20what%20you're%20hoping%20for%20because%20it%20can%20be%20something%20to%20add%20to%20a%20portfolio%20of%20your%20work%20that%20can%20be%20shown%20to%20future%2C%20potential%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20reach%20out%20to%20family%20members%2C%20friends%20for%20small%20little%20projects%20to%20build%20your%20portfolio%2C%26quot%3B%20Okwulehie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20a%20portfolio%2C%20Okwulehie%20said%20you%20should%20also%20build%20your%20brand%2C%20including%20making%20a%20website.%20Okwulehie%20also%20suggested%20asking%20friends%20and%20early%20clients%20to%20refer%20your%20services%20to%20others%20if%20they're%20happy%20with%20your%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20research%20can%20also%20be%20important.%20Okwulehie%20said%20she%20would%20read%20how%20entrepreneurs%20got%20started.%20She%20said%20reading%20stories%20helped%20her%20have%20the%20confidence%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20She%20also%20found%20listening%20to%20YouTube%20videos%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOkwulehie%20also%20noted%20multitasking%20is%20important%20for%20having%20side%20work.%20She%20said%20if%20the%20work%20is%20something%20you%20can%20do%20digitally%20like%20from%20your%20phone%20to%20use%20the%20time%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20you're%20on%20the%20bus%20or%20you're%20commuting%20or%20you're%20doing%20laundry%20or%20the%20kids%20are%20about%20to%20go%20to%20sleep%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20some%20work%20on%20your%20business%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20just%20have%20to%20be%20highly%20motivated%20and%20love%20what%20you%20do%20to%20make%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20found%20being%20able%20to%20pursue%20a%20side%20business%20while%20holding%20a%20full-time%20job%20rewarding%20and%20comes%20with%20several%20benefits%2C%20including%20being%20beneficial%20for%20her%20family%20and%20herself%20as%20well%20as%20being%20able%20to%20work%20on%20financial%20goals%20more%20effectively%20given%20the%20additional%20income.%20A%20major%20benefit%20has%20also%20been%20being%20able%20to%20grow%20personally%20and%20professionally%20because%20she%20can%20test%20ideas%20and%20build%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20having%20a%20side%20business%20has%20enriched%20our%20lives%20both%20financially%20and%20personally%2C%20contributing%20to%20our%20overall%20well-being%20and%20quality%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Okwulehie%20said.%20%26quot%3BMost%20notably%2C%20it%20has%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20building%20generational%20wealth%20for%20our%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHow%20much%20have%20you%20made%20from%20a%20side%20business%20or%20side%20hustle%3F%20Have%20you%20turned%20a%20side%20hustle%20or%20business%20into%20your%20main%20or%20only%20source%20of%20income%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20to%20share%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emhoff%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fside-hustle-main-income-how-to-build-profitable-business-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709379781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e22fbb90413ab8e1d8773d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F