r%20private%20medical%20colleges%20have%20been%20granted%20permissions%20last%20year%2C%20in%202023.%20Of%20the%20508%20new%20nursing%20schools%20and%20colleges%20set%20up%20over%20two%20years%2C%20only%20one%20was%20on%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20initiative%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2FMar%2F02%2Fno-new-govt-med-colleges-built-in-gujarat-since-95-but-nod-to-4-in-23%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBhavnagar%2520in%25201995.-%2CThus%252C%2520the%2520Gujarat%2520government%2520has%2520not%2520had%2520a%2520single%2520government%2Ca%2520go%252Dahead%2520in%25202023.%5C%22%3Ereports%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20BJP%20state%20government%2C%20in%20power%20almost%20continuously%20since%201995%2C%20but%20for%20a%20brief%20interlude%2C%20said%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20that%20six%20government%20medical%20colleges%20are%20operating%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20first%20was%20established%20in%20Ahmedabad%20in%201871%20and%20the%20last%20in%20Bhavnagar%20in%201995.%20This%20was%20in%20response%20to%20Congress%20MLA%20Amit%20Chavda%E2%80%99s%20question%20in%20the%20Assembly%20on%20Thursday%2C%20February%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reply%20also%20says%20no%20government%20medical%20colleges%20were%20approved%20in%202022%20or%202023%2C%20but%20four%20private%20medical%20colleges%20were%20given%20the%20green%20signal%20last%20year.%20%C2%A0The%20newspaper%20reports%20that%20in%202022%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfive%20medical%20colleges%20run%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20Medical%20Education%20%26amp%3B%20Research%20Society%20(a%20registered%20trust%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20government)%20got%20government%20approval.%E2%80%9D%20Also%2C%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20no%20new%20government%20or%20grant-aided%20college%20for%20Ayurveda%20and%20Homeopathy%20degrees%20has%20been%20sanctioned%20in%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20one%20public%20nursing%20school%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20another%20question%20raised%20by%20Congress%20MLA%20Ganiben%20Thakor%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20stated%20that%20508%20new%20nursing%20schools%20and%20colleges%20have%20opened%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20but%20of%20the%20508%2C%20only%20one%20is%20a%20public%20nursing%20institution.%20The%20remaining%20507%20were%20all%20private%20colleges.%20In%202023-24%2C%20of%20a%20total%20of%20315%20institutes%20established%2C%20only%20one%2C%20MSC%20Nursing%20Government%20College%2C%20was%20government-run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20Minister%20Rushikesh%20Patel%20claimed%20that%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20establish%20a%20medical%20college%20in%20each%20district.%20%E2%80%9CBy%202027%2C%20the%20government%20aims%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20medical%20seats%20at%20undergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20levels%20to%2012%2C200%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20health%20minister%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fees%20of%20government%20colleges%20must%20be%20low%20compared%20to%20private%20colleges%20to%20enable%20the%20poor%20and%20middle-class%20students%20to%20become%20doctors%2C%20but%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20not%20established%20any%20new%20government%20medical%20college%20in%20the%20last%2029%20years%20because%20this%20government%20cares%20only%20for%20rich%20and%20industrialists%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20Chavda%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20Assembly%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20medical%20institutions%20outside%20Gujarat%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20country%2C%20as%20the%20country%20gears%20up%20for%20the%20general%20elections%20due%20in%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20amped%20up%20its%20publicity%20but%20there%20has%20been%20a%20sharp%20debate%20on%20exactly%20how%20many%20public%20medical%20institutions%2C%20especially%20AIIMS%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20been%20claiming%20it%20has%20set%20up.%20Five%20were%20inaugurated%20by%20PM%20Modi%20across%20India%2C%20but%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpm-modi-to-inaugurate-5-aiims-next-week-but-are-they-new%5C%22%3Equestions%20about%20how%20%E2%80%98new%E2%80%99%20they%20are%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20of%20multiple%20inaugurations%20they%20have%20seen.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fpm-modi-aiims-functioning%5C%22%3Ereported%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20partially%20constructed%20AIIMS%20being%20declared%20as%20complete%20institutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709373542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F02151450%2FUntitled-design-23-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fno-government-medical-college-set-up-in-gujarat-after-1995-bjp-state-govt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20government%2C%20in%20power%20since%201995%2C%20has%20said%20in%20the%20Assembly%20that%20the%20last%20public%20medical%20college%20in%20the%20state%20was%20in%20Bhavnagar%20in%201995.%20Of%20508%20nursing%20institutions%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20only%20one%20is%20a%20public%20institution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fno-government-medical-college-set-up-in-gujarat-after-1995-bjp-state-govt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20Ukrainian%20general%20eyes%20leadership%20shake-up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709373438000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F12EBA%2Fproduction%2F_132789477_ambulance.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68455874%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gen%20Oleksandr%20Syrs