ade-historians-scramble-to-capture-woodstocks-voices%2Famp_articleshow%2F108161066.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpeace-music-and-memories-as-the-1960s-fade-historians-scramble-to-capture-woodstocks-voices%2Famp_articleshow%2F108161066.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ship%20From%20China%20To%20Pak%20Stopped%20At%20Mumbai%20Port%20Over%20Suspected%20Nuclear%20Cargo%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Karachi-bound%20ship%20from%20China%20was%20stopped%20by%20Indian%20security%20agencies%20at%20Mumbai's%20Nhava%20Sheva%20port%20on%20suspicion%20that%20it%20contained%20a%20dual-use%20consignment%20that%20could%20be%20used%20for%20Pakistan's%20nuclear%20and%20ballistic%20missile%20programme%2C%20officials%20here%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20customs%20officials%2C%20based%20on%20an%20intelligence%20input%2C%20halted%20a%20Malta-flagged%20merchant%20ship%20--%20CMA%20CGM%20Attila%20--%20at%20the%20port%20en%20route%20to%20Karachi%20on%20January%2023%20and%20inspected%20the%20consignment%2C%20which%20included%20a%20Computer%20Numerical%20Control%20(CNC)%20machine%2C%20originally%20manufactured%20by%20an%20Italian%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECNC%20machines%20are%20basically%20controlled%20by%20a%20computer%20and%20produce%20a%20scale%20of%20efficiency%2C%20consistency%20and%20accuracy%20not%20possible%20manually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20also%20inspected%20the%20consignment%20and%20certified%20that%20it%20could%20be%20used%20by%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20for%20its%20nuclear%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20experts%2C%20the%20equipment%20would%20be%20useful%20in%20manufacturing%20critical%20parts%20for%20Pakistan's%20missile%20development%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%201996%2C%20CNC%20machines%20have%20been%20included%20in%20the%20Wassenaar%20Arrangement%20--%20an%20international%20arms%20control%20regime%20aimed%20at%20stopping%20the%20proliferation%20of%20equipment%20with%20both%20civilian%20and%20military%20uses.%20India%20is%20among%20the%2042%20member%20countries%20that%20exchange%20information%20on%20transfers%20of%20conventional%20weapons%20and%20dual-use%20goods%20and%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CNC%20machine%20was%20used%20by%20North%20Korea%20in%20its%20nuclear%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20port%20officials%2C%20with%20specific%20intelligence%2C%20had%20alerted%20the%20Indian%20defence%20authorities%20who%20inspected%20the%20heavy%20cargo%20and%20reported%20their%20suspicions%2C%20after%20which%20the%20consignment%20was%20seized%2C%20the%20officials%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20seizure%20falls%20under%20the%20prevention%20of%20possible%20proliferation%20by%20Pakistan%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20documents%20such%20as%20bills%20of%20loading%20and%20other%20details%20of%20the%20consignment%2C%20the%20consigner%20was%20mentioned%20as%20%26quot%3BShanghai%20JXE%20Global%20Logistics%20Co%20Ltd%26quot%3B%20and%20consignee%20was%20%26quot%3BPakistan%20Wings%20Pvt%20Ltd%26quot%3B%20of%20Sialkot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20deeper%20investigation%20by%20the%20security%20agencies%20indicated%20that%20the%20consignment%2C%20weighing%2022%2C180%20kilogrammes%2C%20was%20shipped%20by%20Taiyuan%20Mining%20Import%20and%20Export%20Co%20Ltd%20and%20was%20meant%20for%20Cosmos%20Engineering%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20instance%20when%20Indian%20port%20officials%20have%20seized%20such%20dual-use%20military-grade%20items%20being%20shipped%20from%20China%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECosmos%20Engineering%2C%20a%20Pakistani%20defence%20supplier%2C%20has%20been%20on%20a%20watchlist%20since%20March%2012%2C%202022%2C%20when%20Indian%20authorities%20intercepted%20a%20shipment%20of%20Italian-made%20thermoelectric%20instruments%2C%20once%20again%20at%20the%20Nhava%20Sheva%20port.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20there%20have%20been%20concerns%20that%20Pakistan%20might%20be%20utilising%20China%20as%20a%20conduit%20to%20acquire%20restricted%20items%20from%20Europe%20and%20the%20US%2C%20masking%20identities%20to%20evade%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20have%20intensified%20over%20Chinese%20support%20for%20Pakistan's%20nuclear%20and%20missile%20programmes%2C%20exemplified%20by%20a%202020%20case%20where%20an%20industrial%20autoclave%2C%20crucial%20for%20missile%20production%2C%20was%20concealed%20as%20industrial%20equipment%20on%20a%20Chinese%20vessel%20bound%20for%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20investigation%20aims%20to%20determine%20if%20the%20suspected%20Pakistani%20entities%20receiving%20these%20dual-use%20items%20are%20supplying%20these%20to%20the%20Defence%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Organisation%20(DESTO)%2C%20responsible%20for%20much%20of%20Pakistan's%20defence%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20assertions%20of%20commitment%20to%20international%20conventions%20by%20both%20Pakistan%20and%20China%2C%20the%20interception%20of%20such%20covert%20shipments%20underscores%20a%20persistent%20cooperation%20in%20potential%20proliferation%20activities%2C%20contravening%20global%20agreements%20and%20regulations%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202020%2C%20China%20was%20supplying%20autoclave%20to%20Pakistan%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20%26quot%3Bindustrial%20dryer%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20autoclave%20was%20seized%20from%20a%20Chinese%20ship%20--%20Dai%20Cui%20Yun%20--%20carried%20a%20Hong%20Kong%20flag%20and%20had%20left%20Jiangyin%20port%20on%20the%20Yangtze%20river%20in%20Jiangsu%20province%20of%20China%2C%20bound%20for%20Pakistan's%20Port%20Qasim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seizure%20of%20the%20autoclave%2C%20possibly%20meant%20to%20be%20used%20in%20the%20missile%20programme%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20strengthens%20apprehensions%20that%20Pakistan%20is%20unabashedly%20indulging%20in%20illegal%20trade%20of%20missiles%20and%20violating%20the%20Missile%20Technology%20Control%20Regime%20(MTCR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20the%20US%20Bureau%20of%20Industry%20and%20Security%20(BIS)%20sanctioned%20three%20Chinese%20companies%20--%20General%20Technology%20Limited%20(autoclave%20supplier%20to%20Pakistan)%2C%20Beijing%20Luo%20Luo%20Technology%20Development%2C%20and%20Changzhou%20Utek%20Composite%20Company%20for%20its%20involvement%20in%20supplying%20missile-applicable%20items%20to%20Pakistan's%20ballistic%20missile%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709372940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-02%2F8gth80us_port-generic-istock-650_625x300_05_February_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fship-from-china-to-pak-stopped-at-mumbai-port-over-suspected-nuclear-cargo-5162226%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Karachi-bound%20ship%20from%20China%20was%20stopped%20by%20Indian%20security%20agencies%20at%20Mumbai's%20Nhava%20Sheva%20port%20on%20suspicion%20that%20it%20contained%20a%20dual-use%20consignment%20that%20could%20be%20used%20for%20Pakistan's%20nuclear%20and%20ballistic%20missile%20programme%2C%20officials%20here%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fship-from-china-to-pak-stopped-at-mumbai-port-over-suspected-nuclear-cargo-5162226%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fship-from-china-to-pak-stopped-at-mumbai-port-over-suspected-nuclear-cargo-5162226%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fship-from-china-to-pak-stopped-at-mumbai-port-over-suspected-nuclear-cargo-5162226%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20least%209%20More%20MLAs%20In%20Touch%20With%20Us%3A%20Disqualified%20Himachal%20Congress%20MLA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERajinder%20Rana%2C%20one%20of%20the%20six%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Congress%20MLAs%20who%20cross-voted%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20was%20later%20disqualified%20from%20the%20assembly%2C%20today%20rubbished%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu's%20claim%20that%20some%20rebel%20legislators%20want%20to%20return%2C%20asserting%20that%20at%20least%20nine%20party%20legislators%20were%20in%20touch%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20accused%20Mr%20Sukhu%20of%20misleading%20people%20with%20his%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20wants%20to%20return.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20at%20least%20nine%20more%20MLAs%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rana%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Mr%20Sukhu%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3B80%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Congress%20is%20together%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20rest%20were%20dissatisfied%20over%20%26quot%3Btrivial%20issues%26quot%3B.%20He%20claimed%20that%20he%20held%20discussions%20with%20the%20six%20disqualified%20MLAs%20and%20the%20situation%20would%20%26quot%3Bsurely%20get%20better%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20coordination%20committee%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20cross-voting%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20for%20the%20lone%20seat%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Mr%20Rana%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20took%20this%20decision%20to%20uphold%20the%20honour%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20its%20people.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BDid%20the%20Congress%20not%20have%20any%20candidate%20from%20the%20party%20workers%20in%20the%20state%20who%20could%20represent%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20pos