mount%20of%20Rs%2052.75%20lakh%20for%204.22%20lakh%20bags%20and%20for%20Mizoram%2C%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20is%20being%20spent%20for%20procuring%201.75-lakh%20such%20bags%2C%20as%20per%20the%20RTI%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sikkim%2C%20the%20process%20is%20pending%20as%20bags%20are%20still%20being%20produced%20while%20a%20private%20company%20has%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20supply.%20The%20FCI%20is%20looking%20to%20procure%2098%2C000%20bags%20at%20Rs%2014.65%20apiece%2C%20totalling%20Rs%2014.35%20lakh%20in%20this%20eastern%20state%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20added%2C%20as%20per%20the%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20per%20piece%20procurement%20cost%20of%20the%20bags%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20logo%20is%20slightly%20different%20in%20each%20state.%20While%20each%20bag%20in%20Sikkim%20is%20being%20bought%20by%20the%20FCI%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2014.65%2C%20in%20Mizoram%20and%20Tripura%20it%20is%20at%20Rs%2014.30%20apiece%2C%20Rs%2012.5%20per%20per%20bag%20in%20Meghalaya%20and%20Rs%2012.375%20per%20bag%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpre-election-pm-modi-logos-on-pds-grain-bags-to-cost-crores-report%5C%22%3EPre-Election%20%E2%80%98PM%20Modi%20Logos%E2%80%99%20on%20PDS%20Grain%20Bags%20to%20Cost%20Crores%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fahead-of-election-fci-starts-process-to-procure-bags-with-photos-of-pm-modi-for-foodgrain-distribution%2Farticle67853977.ece%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20FCI%20had%20directed%20all%20of%20its%2026%20regional%20offices%20to%20float%20tenders%20for%20procuring%20woven%20laminated%20bags%20with%C2%A0%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20logo%20for%20distribution%20of%20food%20grains%20under%20the%20PMGKAY%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20free%20grain%20di