ech-cannot-centre-demands-explanation-after-google-delists-several-indian-apps-from-play-store%2Farticleshow%2F108159073.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20delisted%20well-known%20India%20apps%20from%20Play%20Store.%20IT%20minister%20Vaishnaw%20said%20developers%20%26amp%3B%20affected%20firms%20called%20for%20a%20meeting%20next%20week%20for%20dispute%20resolution.%20Startup%20ecosystem%20key%20to%20Indian%20economy%2C%20fate%20shouldn't%20be%20left%20to%20big%20tech.%20India%20will%20protect%20startups.%20Dispute%20over%20service%20fee%2C%20popular%20matrimony%20apps%20and%20well-known%20startup%20founders%20affected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fbig-tech-cannot-centre-demands-explanation-after-google-delists-several-indian-apps-from-play-store%2Farticleshow%2F108159073.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre's%20Latest%20Move%20After%20Google%20Removes%20Indian%20Apps%20From%20Play%20Store%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIT%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20has%20invited%20representatives%20from%20Google%20for%20a%20meeting%20on%20Monday%20over%20a%20dispute%20between%20the%20tech%20giant%20and%20some%20Indian%20companies%20over%20non-compliance%20with%20billing%20policies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20on%20Friday%20removed%20apps%20from%2010%20Indian%20companies%2C%20citing%20disputes%20over%20service%20fee%20payments.%20Among%20the%20affected%20apps%20were%20matrimony%20services%20such%20as%20Bharat%20Matrimony%20and%20job%20search%20app%20Naukri%2C%20intensifying%20the%20long-standing%20grievances%20of%20Indian%20startups%20against%20Google's%20practices%2C%20including%20in-app%20fee%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaishnaw%2C%20expressing%20optimism%20about%20a%20swift%20resolution%2C%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20hopeful%20that%20Google%20will%20be%20reasonable%20in%20its%20approach.%20We%20have%20a%20large%2C%20growing%20startup%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20it's%20crucial%20to%20protect%20their%20interests.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20already%20asked%20Google%20to%20meet%20me.%20We%20will%20take%20all%20necessary%20steps%20to%20safeguard%20our%20startup%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20I%20trust%20that%20Google%2C%20which%20has%20adapted%20well%20to%20digital%20payments%2C%20will%20approach%20this%20matter%20reasonably%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IT%20Minister%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDispute%20Explained%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20revolves%20around%20attempts%20by%20Indian%20startups%20to%20resist%20Google's%20imposition%20of%20a%20fee%20ranging%20from%2011%20per%20cent%20to%2026%20per%20cent%20on%20in-app%20payments%2C%20following%20an%20order%20from%20antitrust%20authorities%20to%20dismantle%20the%20previous%20fee%20structure%20of%2015%20per%20cent%20to%2030%20per%20cent.%20Google%20says%20that%20its%20fees%20contribute%20to%20the%20development%20and%20promotion%20of%20the%20Android%20and%20Play%20Store%20app%20ecosystem.%20Although%20two%20court%20decisions%20in%20January%20and%20February%20seemingly%20allowed%20Google%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20new%20fee%20or%20remove%20apps%2C%20Indian%20companies%20continue%20to%20contest%20this%20imposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatrimony.com%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Bharat%20Matrimony%2C%20Christian%20Matrimony%2C%20Muslim%20Matrimony%2C%20and%20Jodii%2C%20expressed%20dismay%20as%20its%20matchmaking%20apps%20were%20taken%20down%20from%20Google's%20Play%20Store.%20Founder%20Murugavel%20Janakiraman%20referred%20to%20it%20as%20a%20dark%20day%20for%20India's%20internet%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20potential%20widespread%20impact%20on%20matrimony%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20apps%20are%20getting%20deleted%20one%20by%20one.%20It%20literally%20means%20all%20the%20top%20matrimony%20services%20will%20be%20deleted%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Janakiraman%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20is%20significant%20as%20matrimonial%20apps%20and%20websites%20have%20gained%20popularity%20in%20India%2C%20particularly%20among%20younger%20generations%20opting%20for%20non-traditional%20matchmaking.%20Bharat%20Matrimony%20alone%20boasted%20more%20than%2050%20million%20downloads%20and%20a%20customer%20base%20exceeding%2040%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20actions%20weren't%20limited%20to%20matrimony%20apps.%20Info%20Edge%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20job%20search%20app%20Naukri%20and%20real%20estate%20search%20platform%2099acres%2C%20faced%20removal%20from%20the%20Play%20Store%20as%20well.%20Despite%20initial%20share%20price%20fluctuations%2C%20both%20Matrimony.com%20and%20Info%20Edge%20managed%20to%20recover%20partially%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Alphabet%20Inc.%2C%20defended%20its%20actions%2C%20claiming%20that%2010%20Indian%20companies%20had%20opted%20not%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bimmense%20value%20they%20receive%20on%20Google%20Play%26quot%3B%20for%20an%20extended%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20giving%20these%20developers%20more%20than%20three%20years%20to%20prepare%2C%20including%20three%20weeks%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20order%2C%20we%20are%20taking%20necessary%20steps%20to%20ensure%20our%20policies%20are%20applied%20consistently%20across%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20as%20we%20do%20for%20any%20form%20of%20policy%20violation%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20Google%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fintl%2Fen-in%2Fproducts%2Fplatforms%2Fupholding-a-fair-and-equitable-experience-for-indias-thriving-digital-ecosystem%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20giant%2C%20which%20holds%20a%20dominating%2094%20per%20cent%20share%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%20through%20its%20Android%20platform%2C%20argued%20that%20allowing%20selective%20developers%20to%20evade%20fees%20creates%20an%20uneven%20playing%20field.%20Google%20maintained%20that%20no%20court%20or%20regulator%20had%20disputed%20its%20right%20to%20charge%20fees%20on%20its%20Play%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709369160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F68bkojd_ashwini-vaishnaw-ndtv-_625x300_02_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-latest-move-after-google-removes-indian-apps-from-play-store-5161883%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IT%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20has%20invited%20representatives%20from%20Google%20for%20a%20meeting%20on%20Monday%20over%20a%20dispute%20between%20the%20tech%20giant%20and%20some%20Indian%20companies%20over%20non-compliance%20with%20billing%20policies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-latest-move-after-google-removes-indian-apps-from-play-store-5161883%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-latest-move-after-google-removes-indian-apps-from-play-store-5161883%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-latest-move-after-google-removes-indian-apps-from-play-store-5161883%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BCCI%20Chief%20Selector%20Agarkar%20Was%20Furious%20With%20Iyer%20For%20This%20Reason%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20last%20one%20week%2C%20the%20one%20news%20which%20has%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20noise%20is%20the%20exclusion%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20BCCI's%20latest%20annual%20contract%20list.%20The%20two%20stars%20have%20been%20strongly%20in%20BCCI%20scheme%20of%20things%20in%20the%20past%20one%20year.%20They%20were%20part%20of%20important%20events%20and%20till%20very%20recently%20played%20in%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20Ishan%20Kishan%20was%20last%20part%20of%20the%20squad%20that%20toured%20South%20Africa%20before%20he%20went%20on%20a%20break%20while%20Iyer%20was%20part%20of%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20against%20England%2C%20before%20he%20was%20dropped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reluctance%20of%20the%20duo%20to%20play%20domestic%20cricket%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20reason%20behind%20their%20exclusion.%20Kishan%20after%20going%20on%20break%20trained%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20missed%20Ranji%20Trophy%20matches%20for%20his%20state%20team%20Jharkhand.%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20missed%20a%20Ranji%20Trophy%20game%20for%20his%20state%20team%20Mumbai%20and%20claimed%20he%20was%20unfit.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20Indian%20express%2C%20the%20NCA%20report%20on%20him%20was%20contradictory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20reports%20have%20claimed%20that%20Iyer%20attended%20a%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20pre-IPL%20camp%20during%20this%20time.%20Iyer%20is%20the%20skipper%20of%20KKR.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frevsportz.in%2Fcortisone-shots-60-ball-per-session-playing-through-pain-has-shreyas-iyer-been-treated-unfairly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERevsportz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BCCI%20chief%20selector%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajit%20Agarkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fp