urth%20largest%20consumer%20market%20is%2C%20than%20Uday%20Prakash.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20translator%20Jason%20Grunebaum%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20read%20Uday%20Prakash%20is%20to%20witness%20profound%20displacement.%20It%20is%20a%20displacement%20unleashed%20by%20forces%20both%20imported%20and%20indigenous%2C%20in%20the%20India%20of%20today%20%E2%80%93%20global%2C%20hungry%2C%20late-stage%20capitalism%20steeped%20in%20centuries-old%20caste%20oppression%20%E2%80%93%20inscribed%20on%20the%20likes%20of%20sweepers%2C%20weavers%2C%20semi-retired%20judges%2C%20typesetters%2C%20servants%20returned%20from%20the%20dead%2C%20sick%20slum%20kids%2C%20and%20others%20unable%2C%20or%20unwilling%2C%20to%20fall%20in%20line.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrakash%E2%80%99s%20surreal%20dystopias%20string%20together%20news%20headlines%2C%20history%20and%20poetry.%20There%20is%20no%20justice%2C%20poetic%20or%20otherwise%20in%20the%20economic%20dystopias%20of%20those%20living%20in%20slums%20and%20footpaths%20of%20society.%20Life%20is%20cheap%2C%20people%20are%20always%20dying.%20They%20drink%20discarded%20poison%20syrups%20and%20die%2C%20get%20killed%20in%20encounter%20killings%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETepchu%2C%20Dilli%20ki%20Diwar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%20commit%20suicide%20due%20to%20caste%20oppression%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMohandas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%20die%20screaming%20when%20forced%20to%20doctor%20post-mortem%20reports%2C%20or%20simply%20vanish.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20spiffy%2C%20beautified%2C%20segregated%20city%2C%20in%20Geetanjali%20Shree%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EYahan%20Haathi%20Rahte%20The%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20young%20employee%20in%20a%20multinational%20is%20intrigued%20by%20the%20figure%20of%20an%20old%20lady%20who%20he%20often%20comes%20across%20on%20the%20beau