n%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20traders%2C%20to%20save%20more.%20The%20traders%20found%20newer%20ways%20to%20cross%20the%20police%20barriers%2C%20while%20the%20police%20tried%20to%20enter%20as%20many%20trucks%20as%20possible%20to%20check%20health%20documents%20of%20the%20animals%20and%20the%20arrangements%20for%20their%20fodder%20and%20water.%20Any%20laxity%20led%20to%20a%20case%20lodged%20under%20specific%20clauses%20of%20Prevention%20of%20Cruelty%20to%20Animals%20Act%2C%20due%20to%20which%20the%20animals%20were%20held%20back%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20But%20the%20business%20never%20stopped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20work%20for%20the%20country%20on%20a%20more%20dependable%20basis%2C%20Dhama%20Chero%20had%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20politics%2C%20set%20up%20a%20cow-shelter%2C%20and%20was%20now%20a%20registered%20cow-protector%2C%20%E2%80%9Cgausevak.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mechanics%20that%20connect%20cow%20politics%20to%20upward%20mobility%20and%20quick%20profits%20are%20laid%20bare.%20Opting%20out%20of%20this%20politics%20can%20reduce%20a%20man%20to%20mere%20fodder%20in%20the%20perpetual%20brutal%20struggle%20between%20the%20State%20and%20the%20Naxalites.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20price%20of%20co-option%20also%20keeps%20getting%20raised%20for%20ambitious%20youth%20like%20Dhama%20Chero.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20these%20Hindi%20novels%2C%20the%20eye%20watching%20the%20march%20of%20events%20is%20not%20that%20of%20a%20baffled%20outsider%2C%20but%20of%20an%20insider%3B%20of%20someone%20caught%20in%20a%20nightmare%20they%20have%20no%20ability%20to%20control.%20Like%20Partition%20narratives%2C%20these%20stories%20record%2C%20bear%20witness%2C%20and%20also%20lament%20for%20simpler%2C%20more%20innocent%20times%20when%20all%20shades%20of%20humanity%20could%20exist%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%20way.%20With%20courage%20and%20forthrightness%2C%20they%20perform%20the%20first%20duty%20of%20literature%3A%20%E2%80%9CTo%20tell%20us%20the%20truth%20about%20ourselves%20by%20telling%20us%20lies%20about%20other%20people.%E2%80%9D%20They%20create%20not%20just%20psychic%20spaces%2C%20but%20initiate%20a%20much%20needed%20moral%20discourse%20about%20experiences%20that%20get%20buried%20in%20the%20noise%20of%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERashwita%20Ravy%20is%20the%20pen%20name%20of%20the%20author%2C%20a%20literature%20lover.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709346611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26130445%2FIMG_2925-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwhat-contemporary-hindi-literature-tells-us-about-the-politics-of-hate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Between%20their%20pages%2C%20individual%20anxiety%2C%20grief%2C%20social%20uncertainty%20and%20absurdity%20get%20a%20place%20to%20be.%20These%20books%20show%20us%20how%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20bogey%20of%20an%20enemy%20is%20essential%20to%20ensure%20that%20patriarchy%20and%20caste%20hegemonies%20stay%20intact.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwhat-contemporary-hindi-literature-tells-us-about-the-politics-of-hate%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kaylen%20Ng%20Wins%202024%20Deutsche%20Bank%20Frieze%20Los%20Angeles%20Film%20Award%2C%20Britt%20Williams%20Lands%20Audience%20Award%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709346600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Ffrieze.png%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235928085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kaylen%20Ng%C2%A0was%20named%20as%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20%2410%2C000%20Deutsche%20Bank%20Frieze%20Los%20Angeles%20Film%20Award%20on%20Friday%20at%20the%20renowned%20ar