inevitable%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20at%20least%20576%2C000%20people%20are%20%E2%80%9Cfacing%20catastrophic%20levels%20of%20deprivation%20and%20starvation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20military%20claimed%20that%20soldiers%20only%20fired%20at%20a%20small%20group%20that%20swarmed%20a%20checkpoint%20and%20that%20the%20rest%20had%20died%20due%20to%20stampede.%20However%2C%20witnesses%20told%20western%20media%20agencies%20that%20crowds%20around%20the%20food%20trucks%20were%20hit%20by%20bullets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20acting%20director%20al-Awda%20hospital%2C%20Mohammad%20Salha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FInternational%2FwireStory%2Fgaza-doctor-gunfire-accounted-80-wounds-hospital-aid-107715222%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20out%20of%20the%20176%20injured%20treated%2C%20142%20had%20received%20gunshot%20wounds.%20As%20per%20Health%20officials%2C%20at%20least%20112%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20750%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20action%20began%20after%20Hamas%20launched%20attacks%20into%20Israel%20that%20killed%20more%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C200%20people%2C%20with%20240%20others%20taken%20as%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20toll%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20five-month-long%20military%20campaign%20in%20Gaza%20now%20stands%20at%20over%2030%2C000%2C%20with%20more%20than%2071%2C000%20wounded.%20The%20US%20secretary%20of%20defence%20Lloyd%20Austin%20said%20at%20a%20Congressional%20hearing%20that%20around%2025%2C000%20women%20and%20children%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20since%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20backlash%20from%20European%20capitals%20after%20Thursday%E2%80%99s%20killing%20has%20been%20sharp%2C%20with%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20squarely%20blaming%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDeep%20indignation%20at%20the%20images%20coming%20from%20Gaza%20where%20civilians%