y%20be%20appointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20is%20a%20composite%20institution%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20information%20given%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F7825%2F1%2F33_of_2001_%2528e%2529.pdf%5C%22%3Epoint%2010A%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20definition%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Ecomposite%20institution%3C%2Fem%3E%20denotes%20a%20place%20of%20worship%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20customs%20and%20traditions%20common%20and%20jointly%20maintained%20by%20Hindus%20and%20other%20religions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20is%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20this%20issue%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Muzrai%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fno-diversion-of-temple-funds-let-bjp-leaders-read-law-first-ramalinga-reddy-karnataka-minister-for-transport-muzrai%2Farticleshow%2F107917058.cms%5C%22%3ERamalinga%20Reddy%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20viral%20claim%20about%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20introducing%20a%20provision%20to%20appoint%20non-Hindus%20to%20temple%20trusts%20was%20misleading.%20Only%20the%20committees%20of%20Baba%20Budan%20Giri%20Dargah%20in%20Chikmagalur%20district%2C%20Bhootrai%20Chowdeshwari%20and%20Saadat%20Ali%20Dargah%20in%20Shivamogga%20district%20consisted%20of%20members%20from%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20communities%20because%20people%20of%20both%20the%20religions%20prayed%20at%20these%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%2C%20but%20due%20to%20opposition%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20JDS%2C%20it%20could%20not%20be%20passed%20in%20the%20legislative%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22qme%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FKarnataka%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTempleTaxBill%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TempleTaxBill%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbwtDEEkDGI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbwtDEEkDGI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NDTV%20(%40ndtv)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fndtv%2Fstatus%2F1761087964543889496%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Akhila%20Karnataka%20Archakas%20(Priests%E2%80%99)%20Association%20supported%20the%20Bill%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20and%20said%20that%20small%20temples%20were%20short%20of%20funds.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20it%20urged%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20to%20support%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20divert%20tax%20money%20from%20rich%20A%20grade%20temples%20to%20smaller%20temples%20for%20the%20uplift%20of%2036%2C000%20C%20grade%20temples%20in%20the%20state%2C%20categorized%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20All%20Karnataka%20Hindu%20Temple%20Archaka%20(priest)%20Association%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20we%20are%20receiving%20a%20sum%20of%20only%20Rs%205%2C000%20as%20our%20salary%2C%20which%20is%20inclusive%20of%20puja%20materials.%20No%20one%20has%20raised%20a%20strong%20voice%20for%20us%20like%20the%20current%20Muzrai%20minister%20Ramalinga%20Reddy.%20The%20money%20from%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund%20will%20be%20used%20only%20for%20the%20uplift%20of%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99%20grade%20temples%20and%20priests.%20We%20are%20very%20happy%20with%20this%20decision.%E2%80%9D%20The%20association%20also%20decided%20to%20submit%20a%20memorandum%20to%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20leaders%2C%20urging%20them%20not%20to%20oppose%20the%20amendments%20of%20the%20current%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem