el%20cart%20excursions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20keep%20their%20promotion%20activities%20in%20line%20with%20their%20philosophy%2C%20the%20eco-stay%E2%80%99s%20business%20cards%2C%20cookery%20books%2C%20and%20brochures%20on%20hand-made%20recycled%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frajasthan-2-1709299575.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Guests%20can%20enjoy%20craft%20workshops%20including%20tie-dye%2C%20bangle%20making%2C%20pottery%2C%20Mandala%20drawing%20etc%20at%20the%20eco-lodge.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frajasthan-2-1709299575.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frajasthan-2-1709299575-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frajasthan-2-1709299575-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frajasthan-2-1709299575-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frajasthan-2-1709299575-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343664%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGuests%20can%20enjoy%20craft%20workshops%20including%20tie-dye%2C%20bangle%20making%2C%20pottery%2C%20Mandala%20drawing%20etc%20at%20the%20eco-lodge.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20it%20opened%20its%20doors%2C%20the%20eco-stay%20has%20hosted%20over%2015%2C000%20guests%20so%20far.%20With%20an%20average%20of%204.4-star%20reviews%20on%20Google%2C%20the%20place%20has%20become%20a%20favourite%20of%20the%20guests.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20has%20amazing%20food%20and%20is%20a%20great%20place%20t