n%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20desperate%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20need%20urgent%20help%2C%20including%20those%20in%20the%20besieged%20north%20where%20the%20United%20Nations%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20deliver%20aid%20in%20more%20than%20a%20week%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20the%20statement%20released%20by%20Spokesperson%20St%C3%A9phane%20Dujarric.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntense%20Israeli%20bombardment%20from%20air%2C%20land%20and%20sea%20continues%20to%20be%20reported%20across%20much%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20resulting%20in%20further%20civilian%20casualties%2C%20displacement%20and%20destruction%20of%20civilian%20infrastructure%2C%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent%2Fhostilities-gaza-strip-and-israel-flash-update-129%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elatest%20situation%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20UN%20humanitarian%20agency%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unocha.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOCHA.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELife%20is%20draining%20out%20of%20Gaza%20at%20terrifying%20speed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5Wd4w8aurX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5Wd4w8aurX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Martin%20Griffiths%20(%40UNReliefChief)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNReliefChief%2Fstatus%2F1763215562455359648%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFears%20of%20Rafah%20invasion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFears%20persist%20over%20the%20planned%20Israeli%20incursion%20into%20Rafah%2C%20where%20more%20than%20one%20million%20people%20are%20seeking%20shelter%20from%20the%20violence%20sparked%20by%20the%20Ha