njuries%20near%20aid%20trucks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesperation%20among%20Gazans%20has%20multiplied%20as%20aid%20trickles%20into%20the%20enclave%2C%20with%20UN%20officials%20stating%20that%20the%20current%2C%20restricted%20deliveries%20do%20not%20even%20meet%20the%20minimum%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20Thursday%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20more%20than%20100%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20where%20aid%20trucks%20attempted%20to%20deliver%20food%20and%20other%20lifesaving%20supplies%20close%20to%20an%20Israeli%20checkpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitial%20reports%20from%20the%20Gaza%20heath%20ministry%20said%20that%20Israeli%20forces%20had%20fired%20into%20the%20crowd%20of%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Defense%20Force%20said%20soldiers%20had%20opened%20fire%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Climited%20response%E2%80%9D%20to%20deter%20crowds%20from%20advancing%20on%20their%20checkpoint%2C%20but%20news%20reports%20suggest%20that%20amid%20chaotic%20scenes%20and%20a%20scramble%20for%20aid%2C%20many%20casualties%20were%20caused%20by%20trucks%20running%20people%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Dujarric%20briefed%20reporters%20in%20New%20York%20and%20said%20the%20aid%20convoy%20involved%20was%20not%20part%20of%20UN%20operations.%20Responding%20to%20questions%2C%20he%20spelled%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20way%20we%20operate%20right%20now%20is%20not%20safe%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20safe%20for%20those%20who%20delivery%20the%20aid%2C%20it%20is%20not%20safe%20for%20people%20who%20receive%20the%20aid%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20chaotic%2C%20opportunistic%20humanitarian%20operation%20that%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20run.%20We%20want%20to%20see%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20so%20that%20we%20can%20distribute%20aid%20in%20an%20organized%2C%20predictable%20and%20safe%20manner%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20not%20an%20option.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJoint%20appeal%20to%20resume%20funding%20for%20UNRWA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20on%20Thursday%2C%2017%20non-governmental%20organizations%20(NGOs)%20in%20the%20European%20Union%20(EU)%20signed%20a%20joint%20appeal%20to%20restore%20funding%20to%20the%20UN%20relief%20agency%20for%20Palestine%20refugees%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20urge%20the%20EU%20and%20Member%20States%20to%20take%20note%20that%20other%20aid%20agencies%20cannot%20replicate%20UNRWA%E2%80%99s%20central%20role%20in%20the%20humanitarian%20response%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20amidst%20the%20current%20crisis%20many%20will%20struggle%20to%20even%20maintain%20their%20current%20operations%20without%20UNRWA%E2%80%99s%20partnership%20and%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNRWA%2Fstatus%2F1763231037864251735%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20appeal%20comes%20after%20major%20UNRWA%20donors%20suspended%20funding%20following%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20that%20a%20dozen%20staff%20members%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20in%20October%20that%20triggered%20the%20current%20devastating%20war%20in%20the%20enclave.%20The%20donors%20withheld%20funds%20pending%20ongoing%20independent%20UN%20investigations%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20suspension%20of%20funding%20to%20the%20main%20aid%20provider%20for%20millions%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20will%20impact%20life-saving%20assistance%20for%20over%20two%20million%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20UNRWA%2C%20which%20serves%20almost%206%20million%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20Jordan%20and%20Syria%2C%20with%20education%2C%20healthcare%20and%20other%20essential%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20look%20away%20from%20Gaza%2C%E2%80%9D%20OCHA%E2%80%99s%20Mr.%20Petropoulos%20said.%20%E2%80%9CFind%20the%20truth%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20and%20believe%20in%20humanity.%20The%20only%20good%20thing%20war%20can%20do%20is%20to%20end.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1147082%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20UN%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709303414000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21131157%2FGuterres.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-chief-appalled-by-tragic-human-toll-of-gaza-war%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Tragically%2C%20an%20unknown%20number%20of%20people%20lie%20under%20rubble%2C'%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20said%2C%20reiterating%20his%20call%20for%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20and%20unconditional%20release%20of%20all%20the%20hostages%20seized%20during%20the%20Hamas-led%20terror%20attack%20of%20October%207.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-chief-appalled-by-tragic-human-toll-of-gaza-war%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Court%20Orders%20NSO%20Group%20to%20Handover%20Code%20for%20Spyware%2C%20Pegasus%20to%20WhatsApp%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F18140916%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-18-at-2.08.35-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20US%20court%20has%20ordered%20the%20NSO%20group%20to%20hand%20over%20its%20code%20for%20its%20spyware%20products%2C%20including%20Pegasus%2C%20to%20WhatsApp%20as%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20legal%20action%20initiated%20against%20the%20American%20corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta-owned%20WhatsApp%20had%20filed%20a%20suit%20against%20NSO%20Group%20in%202019%20for%20illegally%20piggy-backing%20on%20a%20vulnerability%20in%20WhatsApp%20to%20deliver%20Pegasus%20spyware%20to%20targeted%20phones.%20In%20its%20petition%20before%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20California%2C%20WhatsApp%20has%20accused%20Pegasus%20of%20compromising%20the%20phones%20of%20over%201%2C400%20individuals%20over%20a%20two-week%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSO%20Group%20had%20filed%20a%20petition%20before%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20the%20suit%20should%20be%20dismissed%20and%20that%20they%20were%20entitled%20to%20sovereign%20immunity%20as%20they%20were%20representing%20foreign%20governments.%20The%20Israeli%20firm%20has%20claimed%20that%20it%20has%20only%20sold%20Pegasus%20to%20%E2%80%9Cvetted%20governments%E2%80%9D%20for%20use%20in%20anti-terror%20investigation.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F01%2F09%2Fwhatsapp-green-light-lawsuit-nso-group-supreme-court%2F%5C%22%3Erejected%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20argument%20and%20refused%20to%20block%20WhatsApp%E2%80%99s%20lawsuit%20in%20January%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F29%2Fpegasus-surveillance-code-whatsapp-meta-lawsuit-nso-group%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20on%20Friday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Judge%20Phyllis%20Hamilton%20has%20instructed%20the%20NSO%20Group%20to%20provide%20%E2%80%9Call%20relevant%20spyware%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20period%20of%20one%20year%20before%20and%20after%20the%20purported%20attacks%20on%20WhatsApp%20users%2C%20spanning%20April%2029%2C%202018%2C%20and%20May%2010%2C%202020.%20Additionally%2C%20NSO%20is%20required%20to%20furnish%20WhatsApp%20with%20details%20regarding%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20full%20functionality%20of%20the%20relevant%20spyware%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20judge%2C%20however%2C%20did%20concur%20with%20NSO%E2%80%99s%20argument%20that%2C%20at%20present%2C%20the%20company%20should%20not%20be%20compelled%20to%20disclose%20the%20identities%20of%20its%20clients%20or%20details%20concerning%20its%20server%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20WhatsApp%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20court%20ruling%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20milestone%20in%20our%20long-running%20goal%20of%20protecting%20WhatsApp%20users%20against%20unlawful%20attacks%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CSpyware%20companies%20and%20other%20malicious%20actors%20need%20to%20understand%20they%20can%20be%20caught%20and%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20ignore%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20There%20was%20no%20comment%20from%20NSO%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETop%20of%20form%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20powerful%20Pegasus%20spyware%20allows%20access%20to%20smartphones%20and%20their%20entire%20content%2C%20permitting%20remote%20operators%20to%20switch%20on%20their%20microphones%20and%20cameras%20at%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fpegasus-project%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bottom%20of%20Formin%20collaboration%20with%2016%20other%20global%20media%20organisations%20led%20by%20Forbidden%20Stories%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20revealed%20the%20names%20of%20people%20who%20were%20either%20persons%20of%20interest%20or%20forensically%20identified%20as%20having%20been%20targeted%20by%20clients%20of%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fproject-pegasus-list-of-names-uncovered-spyware-surveillance%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20revealed%20the%20names%20of%20161%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20were%20targets%20or%20potential%20targets%20for%20surveillance%20by%20clients%20of%20the%20NSO%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Novem