kpocketing%20and%20luggage%20theft%20cases%20are%20unfortunately%20a%20common%20occurrence%20while%20commuting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20case%20of%20pickpocketing%20made%20Atul%20Gupta%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Arista%20Vault%20rethink%20the%20way%20people%20look%20at%20travel%20safety.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20my%20wallet%20stolen%20on%20the%20Delhi%20metro%20and%20was%20technically%20stranded%20with%20no%20money%20on%20my%20way%20to%20an%20important%20event.%20This%20triggered%20a%20thought%20and%20I%20started%20to%20brainstorm%20ideas%20on%20how%20we%20can%20make%20travelling%20safer%20using%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECo-founded%20by%20Atul%20and%20Purvi%20Roy%2C%20the%20startup%20makes%20products%20that%20make%20our%20travel%20safer.%20From%20smart%20wallets%20to%20luggage%2C%20it%20has%20made%20travelling%20safer%20for%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20duo%20won%20the%20sharks%20over%20at%20the%20TV%20show%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20and%20won%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%2045%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20Unique%20Journey%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20their%20unique%20products%2C%20what%20is%20interesting%20is%20the%20journey%20the%20founders%20had%20before%20collaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2039%2C%20Atul%E2%80%99s%20career%20started%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20youngest%20person%20in%20my%20batch%20to%20clear%20the%20Railways%20exams%20and%20got%20posted%20as%20a%20ticket%20collector.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20was%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20lost%20their%20luggage%20to%20theft.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20distress%20and%20loss%20it%20caused%20to%20the%20people%20and%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22