ional-level%20awards%20for%20her%20remarkable%20efforts.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-4-1709127551.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-4-1709127551-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-4-1709127551-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-4-1709127551-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-4-1709127551-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343503%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20village%20head%20has%20bagged%20several%20national-level%20awards%20for%20her%20remarkable%20efforts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20this%20huge%20village%20makeover%20is%20its%20sarpanch%20Gadge%20Meenakshi.%20For%20her%20remarkable%20efforts%2C%20she%20was%20felicitated%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20ahead%20of%20the%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Day%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20sheds%20light%20on%20how%20she%20achieved%20this%20massive%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20on%20a%20village%20in%20dire%20straits%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20Meenakshi%20herself%20experienced%20the%20lack%20of%20basic%20amenities%20in%20the%20village.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20school%20till%20class%20V%20in%20our%20village.%20For%20higher%20studies%2C%20we%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20go%20out.%20This%20was%20the%20period%20when%20most%20of%20the%20girls%20would%20drop%20out.%20Anyway%2C%20I%20pushed%20myself%20to%20study%20till%20class%2012%20at%20least%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20