nds%20from%20the%20state%20and%20the%20central%20government%20to%20successfully%20implement%20various%20government%20programmes%20and%20achieve%20the%20change.%20Other%20than%20the%20official%20help%2C%20Meenakshi%20credits%20the%20community%20for%20the%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20panchayat%20is%20entitled%20to%20the%20same%20funds%20but%20we%20stood%20apart%20from%20them%20because%20we%20utilised%20them%20for%20betterment.%20But%20this%20success%20could%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20at%20the%20individual%20level.%20Only%20when%20you%20involve%20the%20community%20and%20give%20them%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%2C%20can%20you%20achieve%20a%20drastic%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20seeing%20the%20problems%20of%20this%20village.%20Now%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2040%2C%20I%20have%20witnessed%20it%20getting%20transformed.%20It%20is%20immensely%20satisfying%20to%20be%20able%20to%20see%20my%20village%20transform%20in%20my%20lifetime%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Meenakshi%2C%20who%20is%20now%20working%20on%20producing%20biogas%20at%20the%20village%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20images%3A%20Subhash%20Gadge)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709128630000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-4-1709127551.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343498%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Telangana's%20Mukhra%20K%20village%20has%20emerged%20to%20be%20a%20model%20for%20gram%20panchayats%20across%20India.%20Behind%20this%20award-winning%20model%20is%20its%20sarpanch%20Gadge%20Meenakshi.%20She%20shares%20how%20she%20transformed%20the%20village.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343498%2Fmodel-village-mukhra-k-telangana-was-transformed-by-sarpanch-meenakshi-gadge-womens-da