ts%20biryani%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehas%20gathered%20a%20list%20of%20foods%20you%20should%20try%20other%20than%20the%20epic%20biryani.%20Some%20of%20these%20suggestions%20are%20even%20backed%20by%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20foodies%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Irani%20Chai%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPride%20of%20every%20citizen%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20Irani%20chai%20is%20something%20that%20you%20cannot%20miss.%20Originating%20from%20Persian%20immigrants%20who%20settled%20in%20the%20city%2C%20this%20tea%20carries%20with%20it%20a%20legacy%20that%20spans%20generations.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EServed%20in%20small%20cups%2C%20the%20tea%20is%20a%20blend%20of%20strong%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F201369%2Fblack-rice-himalayas-red-rice-online-manipur-recipe-vegetarian-uttarakhand-lifestyle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earomatic%20black%20tea%3C%2Fa%3E%20infused%20with%20spices%20like%20cardamom%2C%20cloves%2C%20and%20cinnamon%2C%20with%20cream%20simmered%20to%20perfection.%20Usually%20paired%20with%20crisp%2C%20buttery%20Osmania%20biscuits%20or%20decadent%20Irani%20samosas%2C%20sipping%20Irani%20chai%20in%20the%20bustling%20city%20is%20an%20experience%20you%20cannot%20miss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChef%20Sarash%20Goila%2C%20a%20lover%20of%20this%20creamy%20tea%2C%20took%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20to%20express%20his%20love%20for%20the%20chai%20and%20recommended%20Cafe%20Bahar.%20He%20recommends%20sipping%20the%20creamy%20tea%20with%20%E2%80%9COsmania%20biscoot%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIrani%20Chai%20(milky%20sweet%20in%20white%20ceramic%20cup)%20w%20Osmania%20biscoot%20(Rs.%203%20only%2C%20flaky%20savoury)%20at%20Cafe%20Bahar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FHyderabad%3Fsrc%