from%20people%20all%20over%20India%2C%20asking%20her%20whether%20she%20can%20admit%20their%20paraplegic%20dogs.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20from%20Kerala%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Hyderabad%20and%20even%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20call%20us%20to%20ask%20whether%20they%20can%20admit%20paraplegic%20dogs%20into%20our%20shelter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sarah%20with%20her%20dogs.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSarah-Iyer-Dog-Shelter-Image-45-1708958966-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343239%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESarah%20playing%20with%20the%20dogs%20in%20her%20shelter.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDealing%20with%20loss%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20dream%20is%20to%20have%20no%20dogs%20suffer%20on%20the%20streets.%20Backed%20by%20an%20extremely%20robust%20animal%20birth%20control%20program%20and%20proper%20shelters%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20see%20fewer%20dogs%20on%20the%20streets.%20With%20their%20numbers%20on%20the%20street%20reduced%2C%20ther