%20may%20emit%20hazardous%20volatile%20organic%20compounds%20(VOCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20analysis%20highlighted%20that%20many%20of%20these%20VOCs%20pose%20serious%20health%20risks%2C%20including%20damage%20to%20the%20respiratory%20system%2C%20heightened%20cancer%20susceptibility%2C%20and%20adverse%20effects%20on%20developmental%20and%20reproductive%20health.%20Furthermore%2C%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EEnvironmental%20Working%20Group%3C%2Fem%3E%20(EWG)%20cautioned%20that%20the%20fumes%20emanating%20from%20certain%20cleaning%20products%20could%20trigger%20asthma%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimran%20recounts%20that%20during%20the%20first%2010%20to%2012%20weeks%20post-lockdown%2C%20she%2C%20like%20many%20other%20mothers%2C%20found%20herself%20relying%20heavily%20on%20cleaning%20products%20at%20home.%20She%20scrubbed%20surfaces%20multiple%20times%20to%20maintain%20a%20COVID-19-free%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20using%20cleaning%20liquids%20for%20washing%20our%20vegetables%2C%20fruits%20and%20everything%20else%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20hygiene%20took%20centre-stage%2C%20was%20it%20unknowingly%20causing%20more%20harm%20than%20good%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20careful%20assessment%20of%20multiple%20research%20papers%20made%20Simran%20get%20up%20and%20take%20action.%20She%20looked%20for%20safer%20alternatives%2C%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20many%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20same%20prices%20as%20the%20regular%20cleaning%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20becoming%20more%20aware%20of%20ingredients.%20Discovering%20many%20chemical%20names%20in%20everyday%20products%20was%20triggering%20for%20me%2C%20as%20they%20posed%20harm%20to%20my%20daughter.%20While%20doing%20home%20cleaning%2C%20I%20had%20a%20first-hand%20experience%20of%20how%20it%20was%20affecting%20my%20hands.%20I%20could%20see%20exactly%20what%20was%20being%20put%20in%20the%20bucket%2C%E2%80%9D%20Simran%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C