t%20move.%20The%20neighbour%20who%20noticed%20this%20immediately%20told%20Sukhjot%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20Rajinder%20Kaur%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20your%20daughter%20can%20hear.%20Take%20her%20to%20the%20doctor!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajinder%20hurriedly%20took%20her%20two-and-a-half-year-old%20daughter%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20where%20the%20doctor%20diagnosed%20her%20with%20severe%20hearing%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20to%20many%20hospitals%20after%20that%2C%20including%20AIIMS.%20Everyone%20gave%20the%20same%20diagnosis.%20They%20said%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20get%20a%20cochlear%20implant%2C%20which%20would%20cost%20almost%20Rs%206%20to%207%20lakh.%20My%20husband%20is%20an%20auto%20driver%20and%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20fathom%20how%20to%20cough%20up%20such%20a%20big%20amount%20of%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajinder%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20passed%20as%20the%20couple%20visited%20various%20hospitals%20and%20explored%20different%20options.%20In%202014%2C%20when%20the%20child%20was%20five%20years%20old%2C%20they%20were%20introduced%20to%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20which%20offered%20assistance.%20With%20their%20financial%20support%2C%20Sukhjot%20received%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20that%20year%20and%20is%20now%20flourishing%20in%20a%20mainstream%20school%20just%20like%20any%20other%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20can%20now%20speak%20well%20and%20is%20a%20good%20student.%20She%20also%20paints%20very%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajinder%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20yearning%20to%20hear%20her%20speak.%20Now%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20of%20it!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-170878365